        "created_at": "2021-05-04T23:17:14.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>The '15 vintage of Clos des Myglands was a beauty and this is equally as good. Immediately inviting displaying oodles of dark fruits, perfectly ripe and crunchy. There\u2019s some underlying muscle, consistent with its youth, but this will be really humming in 5 to 15 years. In today\u2019s Burgundy market this is a screaming bargain that can be enjoyed now.</p>",
